Company Overview of Cook & Bynum Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Cook & Bynum Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund manager. The firm provides its services to investment companies and other pooled investment vehicles. It launches and manages an equity mutual fund for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets across the globe. It invests in value stocks of companies. Cook & Bynum Capital Management, LLC was founded in 2001 and is based in Birmingham, Alabama.


